        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3060",
        "content": "THE MASTER SMITH",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3060_163499_000004_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3060/163499/3060_163499_000004_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3060",
        "content": "Once on a time, in the days when our Lord and saint Peter used to wander on earth, they came to a smith's house.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3060_163499_000006_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3060/163499/3060_163499_000006_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3060",
        "content": "'Who are you?' he said to the Smith.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3060_163499_000007_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3060/163499/3060_163499_000007_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3060",
        "content": "'Read what's written over the door', said the Smith; 'but maybe you can't read writing.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3060_163499_000007_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3060/163499/3060_163499_000007_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3060",
        "content": "If so, you must wait till some one comes to help you.'",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3060_163499_000008_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3060/163499/3060_163499_000008_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3060",
        "content": "Before our Lord had time to answer him, a man came with his horse, which he begged the Smith to shoe.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3060_163499_000009_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3060/163499/3060_163499_000009_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3060",
        "content": "'Might I have leave to shoe it?' asked our Lord.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3060_163499_000010_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3060/163499/3060_163499_000010_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3060",
        "content": "'You may try, if you like', said the Smith; 'you can't do it so badly that I shall not be able to make it right again.'",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3060_163499_000011_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3060/163499/3060_163499_000011_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3060",
        "content": "So our Lord went out and took one leg off the horse, and laid it in the furnace, and made the shoe red hot; after that, he turned up the ends of the shoe, and filed down the heads of the nails, and clenched the points; and then he put back the leg safe and sound on the horse again.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3060_163499_000011_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3060/163499/3060_163499_000011_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3060",
        "content": "All the while, the Smith stood by and looked on.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3060_163499_000013_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3060/163499/3060_163499_000013_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3060",
        "content": "'Oh, you think so, do you?' said our Lord.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3060_163499_000015_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3060/163499/3060_163499_000015_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3060",
        "content": "'Mark now, what you see', said our Lord.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3060_163499_000016_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3060/163499/3060_163499_000016_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3060",
        "content": "Then he took the woman and laid her in the furnace, and smithied a lovely young maiden out of her.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3060_163499_000017_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3060/163499/3060_163499_000017_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3060",
        "content": "There it stands over my door.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3060_163499_000021_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3060/163499/3060_163499_000021_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3060",
        "content": "Then he laid the legs in the furnace, just as he had seen our Lord lay them, and threw on a great heap of coal, and made his mates work the bellows bravely; but it went as one might suppose it would go. The legs were burnt to ashes, and the Smith had to pay for the horse.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3060_163499_000024_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3060/163499/3060_163499_000024_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3060",
        "content": "But it went no better with the poor old woman than with the horse's legs.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3060_163499_000027_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3060/163499/3060_163499_000027_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3060",
        "content": "'If you might have three wishes from me', said our Lord, 'what would you wish for?'",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3060_163499_000028_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3060/163499/3060_163499_000028_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3060",
        "content": "'Only try me', said the Smith, 'and you'll soon know.'",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3060_163499_000029_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3060/163499/3060_163499_000029_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3060",
        "content": "So our Lord gave him three wishes.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3060_163499_000030_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3060/163499/3060_163499_000030_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3060",
        "content": "'Well', said the Smith, 'first and foremost, I wish that any one whom I ask to climb up into the pear tree that stands outside by the wall of my forge, may stay sitting there till I ask him to come down again.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3060_163499_000030_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3060/163499/3060_163499_000030_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3060",
        "content": "The second wish I wish is, that any one whom I ask to sit down in my easy chair which stands inside the workshop yonder, may stay sitting there till I ask him to get up.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3060_163499_000030_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3060/163499/3060_163499_000030_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3060",
        "content": "Last of all, I wish that any one whom I ask to creep into the steel purse which I have in my pocket, may stay in it till I give him leave to creep out again.'",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3060_163499_000031_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3060/163499/3060_163499_000031_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3060",
        "content": "'You have wished as a wicked man', said saint Peter; 'first and foremost, you should have wished for God's grace and goodwill.'",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3060_163499_000032_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3060/163499/3060_163499_000032_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3060",
        "content": "'I durstn't look so high as that', said the Smith; and after that our Lord and saint Peter bade him 'good bye', and went on their way.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3060_163499_000036_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3060/163499/3060_163499_000036_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3060",
        "content": "So the Devil thanked him for his kind offer, and climbed up into the pear tree.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3060_163499_000038_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3060/163499/3060_163499_000038_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3060",
        "content": "There he was, and there he must stay.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3060_163499_000040_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3060/163499/3060_163499_000040_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3060",
        "content": "'You're ready now, of course', said he; 'you've had time enough to hammer the head of that nail, I should think.'",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3060_163499_000041_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3060/163499/3060_163499_000041_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3060",
        "content": "So while I work at the point, you may just as well sit down in my easy chair and rest yourself; I'll be bound you're weary after coming so far.'",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3060_163499_000042_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3060/163499/3060_163499_000042_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3060",
        "content": "'Thank you kindly', said the Devil, and down he plumped into the easy chair; but just as he had made himself comfortable, the Smith said, on second thoughts, he found he couldn't get the point sharp till four years were out.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3060_163499_000043_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3060/163499/3060_163499_000043_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3060",
        "content": "'Well now, you may get up and be off about your business', and away went the Devil as fast as he could lay legs to the ground.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3060_163499_000045_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3060/163499/3060_163499_000045_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3060",
        "content": "'Now, I know you must be ready.'",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3060_163499_000046_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3060/163499/3060_163499_000046_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3060",
        "content": "Is it true what people say, that the Devil can make himself as small as he pleases?'",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3060_163499_000049_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3060/163499/3060_163499_000049_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3060",
        "content": "'With all my heart', said the Devil, who made himself small in a trice, and crept into the purse; but he was scarce in when the Smith snapped to the clasp.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3060_163499_000052_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3060/163499/3060_163499_000052_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3060",
        "content": "don't you know I'm inside the purse?'",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3060_163499_000055_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3060/163499/3060_163499_000055_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3060",
        "content": "'Very well!' said the Smith; 'now, I think, the links are pretty well welded, and you may come out'; so he unclasped the purse, and away went the Devil in such a hurry that he didn't once look behind him.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3060_163499_000059_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3060/163499/3060_163499_000059_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3060",
        "content": "'Good day', said the Smith; 'whither are you off to?'",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3060_163499_000060_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3060/163499/3060_163499_000060_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3060",
        "content": "'To the kingdom of Heaven', said the Tailor, 'if I can only get into it'--'but whither are you going yourself?'",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3060_163499_000062_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3060/163499/3060_163499_000062_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3060",
        "content": "Then he called the watch, and bade him go and tell the Devil there was some one outside who wished to speak a word with him.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3060_163540_000002_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3060/163540/3060_163540_000002_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3060",
        "content": "A good, easy man he was, but that was just why she thought more of the lad next door, whom they called 'Tom Totherhouse'.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3060_163540_000003_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3060/163540/3060_163540_000003_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3060",
        "content": "'Dare you wager ten dollars, mother, that I don't make you lay bare your own shame?'",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3060_163540_000004_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3060/163540/3060_163540_000004_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3060",
        "content": "'Yes I dare', said she; and so they wagered ten dollars.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3060_163540_000005_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3060/163540/3060_163540_000005_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3060",
        "content": "'What! are we to go home already?' said the man, who hadn't given any heed to what the lad did.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3060_163540_000006_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3060/163540/3060_163540_000006_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3060",
        "content": "'Yes, we must, since mother calls', said the lad.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3060_163540_000007_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3060/163540/3060_163540_000007_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3060",
        "content": "But when they came into the room, there stood a whole bowl of custards on the table.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3060_163540_000008_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3060/163540/3060_163540_000008_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3060",
        "content": "'Nay, nay, mother', cried out the man; 'shall we have custards to day?'",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3060_163540_000009_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3060/163540/3060_163540_000009_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3060",
        "content": "'Yes, that you shall, dear', said the Goody; but she was as sour as verjuice, and as cross as two sticks.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3060_163540_000010_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3060/163540/3060_163540_000010_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3060",
        "content": "So when they had eaten and drank all the good cheer up, off they went again to their work, and the Goody said to Tom:",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3060_163540_000012_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3060/163540/3060_163540_000012_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3060",
        "content": "This the lad stood outside in the passage and listened to.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3060_163540_000013_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3060/163540/3060_163540_000013_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3060",
        "content": "'Do you know, father', he said, 'I think we'd best go down into the hollow and put our fence to rights, which is blown down, before the neighbours' swine get in and root up our meadow.'",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3060_163540_000014_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3060/163540/3060_163540_000014_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3060",
        "content": "'Aye, aye, let's go and do it', said the man; for he did all he was told, good, easy man.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3060_163540_000015_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3060/163540/3060_163540_000015_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3060",
        "content": "So when the afternoon was half spent, down came the Goody sneaking along into the mead, with something under her apron.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3060_163540_000017_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3060/163540/3060_163540_000017_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3060",
        "content": "'Yes, yes, that you shall', she said; but she was sourer and wilder than ever.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3060_163540_000018_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3060/163540/3060_163540_000018_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3060",
        "content": "So they made merry, and crammed themselves with bannocks and butter, and had a drop of brandy into the bargain.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3060_163540_000019_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3060/163540/3060_163540_000019_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3060",
        "content": "'He's had nothing between meals, I'll be bound.'",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3060_163540_000021_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3060/163540/3060_163540_000021_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3060",
        "content": "As he went along the lad broke a bannock to bits, and dropped the crumbs here and there as he walked.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3060_163540_000021_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3060/163540/3060_163540_000021_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3060",
        "content": "But when he got to Tom Totherhouse he said:",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3060_163540_000022_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3060/163540/3060_163540_000022_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3060",
        "content": "He won't stand it any longer, and has sworn to drive his axe into you as soon as ever he can set eyes on you.'",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3060_163540_000023_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3060/163540/3060_163540_000023_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3060",
        "content": "As for Tom, he was so frightened he scarce knew which way to turn, and the lad went back again to his master.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3060_163540_000025_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3060/163540/3060_163540_000025_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3060",
        "content": "His old dame stood in the meadow and looked at him as he did this for a while, and wondered and wondered what it could be her husband was gathering up.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3060_163540_000026_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3060/163540/3060_163540_000026_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3060",
        "content": "'Oh, I know', said the lad, 'master's picking up stones, I'll be bound; for he has marked how often this Tom Totherhouse runs over here; and the old fellow won't stand it any longer; and now he has sworn to stone mother to death.'",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3060_163540_000029_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3060/163540/3060_163540_000029_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3060",
        "content": "'Oh', said the lad, 'maybe the house at home is on fire!'",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3060_163540_000031_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3060/163540/3060_163540_000031_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3060",
        "content": "don't stone me to death; don't stone me to death! and I'll give you my word never to let Tom Totherhouse come near me again.'",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3060_163542_000003_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3060/163542/3060_163542_000003_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3060",
        "content": "INTRODUCTION TO APPENDIX",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3060_163542_000005_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3060/163542/3060_163542_000005_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3060",
        "content": "The Negroes in the West Indies still retain the tales and traditions which their fathers and grandfathers brought with them from Africa. Some thirty years back these 'Ananzi Stories', as they are called, were invariably told at the Negro wakes, which lasted for nine successive nights.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3060_163542_000005_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3060/163542/3060_163542_000005_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3060",
        "content": "The wakes are now, it is believed, almost entirely discontinued, and with them have gone the stories.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3060_163542_000005_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3060/163542/3060_163542_000005_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3060",
        "content": "The translator, whose early childhood was passed in those islands, remembers to have heard such stories from his nurse, who was an African born; but beyond a stray fragment here and there, the rich store which she possessed has altogether escaped his memory.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3060_163542_000005_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3060/163542/3060_163542_000005_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3060",
        "content": "The following stories have been taken down from the mouth of a West Indian nurse in his sister's house, who, born and bred in it, is rather regarded as a member of the family than as a servant.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3060_163542_000005_000009",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3060/163542/3060_163542_000005_000009.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3060",
        "content": "In one story we have 'Boots' to the life, while the man whom he outwits is own brother to the Norse Trolls.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3060_163542_000005_000013",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3060/163542/3060_163542_000005_000013.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3060",
        "content": "Then he went home to the Troll, and begged him to come and see how his swine were going down to Hell.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3060_163542_000005_000014",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3060/163542/3060_163542_000005_000014.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3060",
        "content": "But when the Troll saw the swine's tails sticking out of the ground he wanted to pull them back again, so he caught hold of them and gave a great tug, and then down he fell with his heels up in the air, and the tails in his fist.'",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3060_163542_000006_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3060/163542/3060_163542_000006_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3060",
        "content": "In fact, he is the example which the African tribes from which these stories came, have chosen to take as pointing out the superiority of wit over brute strength.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    }
]